QuestData.Title: The Struggle Persists
QuestData.Description: Malygos and his underlings grow stronger in power with each passing day. And now, our latest assault team has been captured and is being held in the Oculus.$b$bWe must attempt a rescue! Belgaristrasz and his companions are invaluable to our cause.
QuestData.LogDescription: Raelorasz wants you to rescue Belgaristrasz and his companions in the Oculus.
QuestData.RewardText: Listen well, $r.$b$bYour work here has just begun!
